              <description>Returns the value of this basic block's field with the given id. If the given id does not exist or is not a string then an exception is thrown.</description>
              <name>getString</name>
              <operation>Get the data field of this basic block with the given id, making sure it is the correct type.</operation>
              <operation>Return the value of the data field.</operation>
