              <description>Adds the given comment used to generate and provide comment lines to this parser element's parent scanner. The given comment is wrapped into multiple lines to not exceed the maximum columns allowed per line.</description>
              <name>add</name>
              <operation>Add a new comment block to the end of this parser element's list, setting its text to the given text.</operation>
              <return_description></return_description>
              <type>void</type>
            </data>
            <variable>
              <data>
                <description>The commented added to this parser element's list of comments as a new block.</description>
                <initializer></initializer>
