          <function>
            <data>
              <description>Returns rich text that displays all inherited parent classes of this view's class block. If this view's class block does not inherit any classes then this returns an empty string.</description>
              <name>displayParents</name>
              <operation>Create an empty return string.</operation>
              <operation>Make a pointer list of child parent blocks this view's class block contains and make sure it is not empty.</operation>
              <operation>Append a rich text title.</operation>
              <operation>Iterate through all of the parent block pointer list and append each one as rich text.</operation>
              <operation>Return the inheritance rich text.</operation>
